## Verification Plan

### Build Check
```bash
cd c:\Users\adit1\Desktop\auramesh
npm run build
```
Must complete with 0 TypeScript errors.

### Manual Verification (in browser at `http://localhost:3000`)

1. **App Init**: Refresh page → splash screen briefly shows → Dashboard loads with device alias in header → IndexedDB [AuraMeshDB](file:///c:/Users/adit1/Desktop/auramesh/src/services/db.ts#6-24) visible in DevTools → Application → IndexedDB
2. **SOS Flow**: Click SOS button → click again to confirm → click "CONFIRM & BROADCAST" → new critical event appears in Event Feed → IndexedDB `sos_messages` table has a new row
3. **Acoustic Monitoring**: Go to Settings → AKD is enabled → on Dashboard, mic status badge shows ACTIVE → say "help" or "fire" → keyword event appears in feed (Chrome only)
4. **Alert Modalities**: Go to Settings → click "Test Alert" → device vibrates (mobile) + page flashes + TTS reads "Test alert received"
5. **Peers Panel**: Click Peers tab → shows empty state initially → after mesh service boots, the tab updates
6. **Storage Footer**: Footer shows event count; updates every 30 seconds

